### SYSTEM 4: FOCUS MODE

When the player holds Shift (or F key), enter focus mode:
- UFO movement speed reduced to 40%
- UFO hitbox shrinks from ~11px radius to 3px radius (for collision only, not visual)
- A glowing 3px dot appears at UFO center showing the true hitbox
- Energy drains at 5/sec while in focus (cheap enough to use regularly)
- A subtle circular "graze ring" visual appears showing the graze detection radius

Add to input handling (the GAME_KEYS set and key detection):
```javascript
