```

In collision detection, use the smaller hitbox when focusing:
```javascript
const hitRadius = ufo.focusing ? 3 : 8;
```

Render the focus dot and graze ring when focusing:
```javascript
if (ufo.focusing) {
  // Graze ring
  ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(100, 200, 255, 0.3)';
  ctx.beginPath();
  ctx.arc(ufoCx, ufoCy, 12, 0, Math.PI * 2);
  ctx.stroke();
  // Hitbox dot
  ctx.fillStyle = '#ffffff';
  ctx.beginPath();
  ctx.arc(ufoCx, ufoCy, 2, 0, Math.PI * 2);
  ctx.fill();
}
```

