### SYSTEM 6: BOMB SYSTEM

3 bombs per life. Press B to activate. Clears ALL bullets on screen, brief invincibility, screen flash.

Add to UFO state: `bombs: 3`
Add to GAME_KEYS: 'KeyB'

```javascript
function useBomb() {
  if (!ufo || ufo.bombs <= 0) return;
  ufo.bombs--;
  ufo.iframes = 2.0; // 2 seconds invincibility

  // Cancel ALL bullets with score conversion
  let cancelled = 0;
  for (let i = 0; i < BULLET_POOL_SIZE; i++) {
    if (bulletPool[i].alive) {
      spawnScorePickup(bulletPool[i].x, bulletPool[i].y, 5);
      killBullet(bulletPool[i]);
      cancelled++;
    }
  }

  screenShake = 6;
  screenFlashTimer = 0.3; // white flash
  AudioManager.playBomb();

  // Visual: expanding ring
  for (let i = 0; i < 32; i++) {
    const angle = (i / 32) * Math.PI * 2;
    spawnParticle(
      ufo.x + ufo.w/2, ufo.y + ufo.h/2,
      Math.cos(angle) * 200, Math.sin(angle) * 200,
      '#88ffff', 0.5, 2
    );
  }
}
```

In updateUFO, check for bomb input:
```javascript
if (justPressed['KeyB']) useBomb();
```

Render bomb count on HUD (show bomb icons near HP hearts).

Add `playBomb()` to audio.js: a deep bass explosion + high-frequency sweep. Use a 60Hz sine oscillator (0.3s) layered with white noise through a high-pass filter sweeping down.

